14:18.365 --> 14:25.792
orbits, about 150 by 600. So to the extent that, if 
you'll pardon my using the skydiving analogy,

14:27.434 --> 14:39.745
that if a skydiver's parachute doesn't open, he's 
going to hold the power to the plane responsible.

14:40.079 --> 15:05.867
uh we don't feel that nasa was responsible for the 
