something rash, but he'll be content to stay out of

30:19.317 --> 30:36.101
the way, strap in a seat or something, and let the 
crew handle the problem, getting all panicky. And

30:36.161 --> 30:44.353
then, of course, they will trade him for whoever in 
operating some of the facilities in the Shuttle,

30:44.553 --> 30:53.445
that we can be an independent person and not have to 
rely on the food for everything. Using the manned

30:53.465 --> 30:58.872
mobile unit, or the MMU, you were the world's first 
