with the two communication systems, like

31:10.085 --> 31:28.009
sanitation and inflatable run of the balloon. And 
in some of the previous missions, the guys had

31:27.989 --> 31:36.480
trouble even getting the pressure set to work 
properly. You know, we were somewhat

31:36.500 --> 31:38.944
apprehensive. There might be something come up 
that would either cancel the EVAs or bring the

31:38.964 --> 31:46.954
whole mission back early or something like that. 
